title: Wedding guest outfit
description: favorite look i've ever worn. was apprehensive about the flower necklace at first but ended up loving it

items.review: mini flare at the bottom of the dress made it super flattering and easy to move around. not much stretch around the torso area though and the material was thin so wasn't good at hiding the 'belly'
great pair of heels! i have wider feet so it got a little painful for me but i could see this being a super comfortable pair of heels for someone with normal feet. also there's padding on the sole
such a cute and unique necklace. like how the string was long enough to tie a bowtie in the back. flower is pretty too. overall though seems to be made of cheaper materials.

title: Outdoors camping/hiking outfit
description: such a comfy outfit to walk explore nature in!

items.review: not too heavy of a sweatshirt. material is lightweight.
one of my favorite pair of jeans. i'm short and they hit right at the ankles. also not too skinny and not too baggy either.
